album.title: Green Leaves
album.description: Richly detailed macro images of leafy plants, trees, and various forms of plant life. Images from volume thirteen of the Japanese Sozaijiten stock photography series.

album.title: Abstract Light
album.description: Color blurs, motion, and abstract light trails. Bright pulses of color, from neon to streaking traffic lights. Content acquired from morguefile.com.

album.title: Motion graphics and shorts
album.description: A collection of motion graphics, animations, and abstract video shorts from a variety of videographers. Content sponsored by the stock video and photography site Revostock.com.

album.title: Mannequins
album.description: Still (very still) life images of department store mannequins from a variety of photographers. Variety of styles and lighting techniques. All images either free stock photography or creative commons.

album.title: Vibrant Colors
album.description: All the colors of the rainbow reprenseted in a variety of real-world forms, including paint, umbrellas, straws, pencils, and and more. Careful, your eyes may burn after viewing this collection.

album.title: Meritage
album.description: From the grape fields of Napa Valley to a tabletop in your local restaurant, this album collects a variety of images on the topic of wine. Bottles, grapes, glasses, and more. Bottoms up.

album.title: Illuminations
album.description: Lamps, ceiling pendants, light bulbs, neon strips, and street lights. A variety of lighting forms and objects, some antique, some modern. All illuminating in their own way.

album.title: The Open Road
album.description: Dusty roads, middle-America blacktop, and lots of empty space. Images of the open road found at morguefile.com and stock.xchng
